[upbeat jazz music]

1058
01:23:50,085 --> 01:23:52,851
[indistinct conversations in distance]

1059
01:23:56,295 --> 01:24:03,059
[indistinct chatter]

1060
01:24:08,890 --> 01:24:11,768
Sir, do you have a reservation?

1061
01:24:12,623 --> 01:24:13,899
No.

1062
01:24:20,508 --> 01:24:23,103
Uno, is this the gentleman you spoke of?

1063
01:24:23,279 --> 01:24:25,014
Yes sir, it is.

1064
01:24:25,289 --> 01:24:27,402
I want you to behave yourself, understood?

1065
01:24:28,260 --> 01:24:29,414
Yes, sir.

1066
01:24:33,006 --> 01:24:37,518
[upbeat jazz music]

1067
01:24:45,085 --> 01:24:46,721
Good afternoon, gentlemen.

1068
01:24:48,732 --> 01:24:50,436
What the hell happened to you?

1069
01:24:52,808 --> 01:24:55,442
[sighs] Lost a fight.

1070
01:25:00,808 --> 01:25:02,925
So, to what do I owe this pleasure?

1071
01:25:04,208 --> 01:25:05,655
Mr. Giovanni...

1072
01:25:05,923 --> 01:25:07,511
Mr. G is fine.

1073
01:25:08,818 --> 01:25:12,052
Sir, I've come to make
good on my contract.

1074
01:25:22,730 --> 01:25:26,380
Why should I accept this
after all the trauma you put me through?

1075
01:25:32,347 --> 01:25:37,537
I was hoping this little extra would
put any differences we have aside.

1076
01:25:38,201 --> 01:25:39,551
Agreed.

1077
01:25:46,684 --> 01:25:48,481
It's a nice place you have here.

1078
01:25:49,361 --> 01:25:52,137
You ever wanna make a bet,
you know who to come to.

1079
01:25:53,287 --> 01:25:56,706
Thanks sir,
but I think I've given up gambling.

1080
01:26:01,507 --> 01:26:05,549
[hopeful music]

1081
01:26:06,794 --> 01:26:10,444
[Zane] Action, adventure,
and happy endings.

1082
01:26:10,468 --> 01:26:13,984
That's what great stories are made of.

1083
01:26:25,019 --> 01:26:33,019
[light percussive music]

1084
01:26:54,041 --> 01:26:56,816
[Zane] I've always heard that
great writers write what they know.

1085
01:27:01,440 --> 01:27:04,052
I don't know any great writers,
but I do know this.

1086
01:27:04,310 --> 01:27:07,931
Sometimes writer's block
can be your best friend.

1087
01:27:08,639 --> 01:27:16,639
[light percussive music]

